name: Hunting for The Lights
description: Blooming Ponds is an area located in Shimmermist Land, the soils, rocks and plants here are very brightly colored and some even emit light, this is due to the feces produced by light-consuming animals. Basically the light released by the plants here is actually the rest of the nutrients that the plants have consumed while the rocks themselves don't emit too much light but the light is compressed into a pigment that forms the basis of the beautiful colors on the rocks.
